issue.title: Any way to preserve tags with download?
issue.body: This is probably a longshot, but would there be any way you could think of to download files from a myimouto board with the tags written in either the filename or the metadata? I've seen some third-party applications and browser extensions that try to do that, but none of them seem to work with myimouto.

comment.body: Exactly what I was looking for.  Thank you!
